{
  "id": "adv_card_rui_02_03",
  "title": "天動瑠依 3話 新しいお仕事",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――グラビア撮影当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—The day of the photoshoot",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "撮影はどう？\n気になることがあったら教えてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How are things going?\nLet me know if there are any issues.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.433333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 7.933333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "何も問題ありません。カメラマンさんも\n他のスタッフさんも、とても気を遣ってくれてます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everything’s fine. The cameraman\nand all the staff are very helpful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.233333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 15.1333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "その……過激なポージングのオーダーも\nありませんでしたし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They’re not asking for anything‚\nyou know… excessive.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.133333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 20.6333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そんな仕事を俺は受けないって\nでも、実際にやってみないと分からないことはあるよな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wouldn’t have accepted the offer if it was anything like that.\nBut there are certain things that you can’t know for sure beforehand.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "今日、天動さんがいい表情をしてるのを見て\nやっとホッとしたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyway‚ I’m relieved to see\nyour relaxed expression today‚ Tendo-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.933333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 32.8333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "くすっ、{user}さん\nずっと心配そうに私を見てるんだもん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe. {user}-san.\nYou looked so concerned",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 38.3666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっとおかしくて\n笑いそうになっちゃいました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "when you were watching me\nthat it was all I could do to keep myself from laughing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……あの笑顔は、俺を見て笑っていたのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "….So that laughter was because of me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 45.3666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんなさい。でも、楽しいお仕事です\n新しいお仕事、受けてよかったです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry. But I’m enjoying this.\nI’m glad to be able to try out something different.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.333333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "今回の仕事は女性誌の水着グラビアだけど\n男女を問わずに天動さんの魅力が伝わると思うよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today’s job is swimsuit gravure for a women’s magazine‚\nbut I think Tendo-san appeal equally to both male and female audiences.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "本当に、そう思いますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do you really think so?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.666666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 59.6666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんだよ。雑誌の発売が楽しみだ\nあっ、そろそろ撮影再開みたいだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course. I look forward to the magazine being published.\nLooks like they’re resuming the shoot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 70.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "はい、{user}さん\nしっかり私の仕事ぶりを見てて下さいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Excuse me then‚ {user}-san.\nRemember to keep an eye on me working!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 75.9333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "そうすれば、私、きっとまた\nいい表情が出来ますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That would help me\nput on the right expression.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 80.3333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "水着姿の女の子を凝視しろと言われてる\nみたいで、それはちょっと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You mean to let me keep on\nstaring a girl in a swim suit…? That's…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 86.6333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？　……あっ\nそういう意味にとらないで下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? …Ah\nThat’s NOT what I meant!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "顔だけを見て下さい！　首から下はNGです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Look at my face! Nothing from the neck down! It's NG!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 95.6666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "無理を言わないでくれ\nどうしたって視界に入るよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re asking the impossible…\nI just can't help‚ \"they\" comes in to my eyes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 100.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "…………なんだか\n急に恥ずかしくなってきました……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now I’m starting to feel\nreally shy…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃ後半は俺、席外そうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Should I wait outside for the second half?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 105.466666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 109.766666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "だ、ダメです！　{user}さんには\n私の仕事をしっかり監督してもらわないと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-no! {user}-san must be here to keep an eye\non me while I’m working…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 116.366666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "と、遠くからなら……いいですから\n……絶対にいなくならないで下さいよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "J-just do it from a distance.\n…But don’t you dare leave the room!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（あのしっかりした天動さんが）\n（あんなに焦って……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I’ve never seen Tendo-san )\n(look so panic like this before….)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.2,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_camera-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4466.666666666995,
          "startTime": 129.666666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3399.9999999999914,
          "startTime": 128.6
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "（TRINITYAiLEのセンター、天動瑠依も）\n（年相応の普通の女の子なんだな……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(She may be the center of TRINITYAiLE‚)\n(but in many ways Rui Tendo is no different from other girls her age.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_03-rui014.m4a",
      "text": "はい、腕はこんな感じでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
